### Step 4: Receive LP Tokens

You will receive LP tokens representing your share of liquidity.

These tokens can later be:
- staked (future feature)
- held for rewards
- withdrawn to remove liquidity

---

## Risks

- Impermanent loss may occur
- Token price is market-driven
- Liquidity is not guaranteed

---

## Recommendation

Early liquidity providers participate in initial price discovery and ecosystem formation.
